                     n="6"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="1"/>relatalake śrī-netrabhaṭena bhujyamānaka-<num value="1.5">dvy-ardha</num>-pāṭaka peranāṭana-nādavarmi<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/><lb 
                     n="7"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/>tpalagarte <num>daśa</num>-droṇavāpā śivahradikā-śoggavargge nartakī-<num value="0.5">Ardha</num>-pāṭaka <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/><lb 
                     n="8"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/>śrīmete śrī-śarvāntareṇa bhujyamānaka mahattara-śikharādibhiḥ kr̥ṣyamā<supplied reason="lost">ṇaka</supplied><lb 
                     n="9" break="no"/>-<num value="1">pāṭaka</num> vihāra-vāstu-<num value="2">dvayañ</num> ca rollavāyikā-Ugravorake vandya-jñānamatinā <unclear>bh</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ujya</supplied><lb 
                     n="10" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">mā</supplied><unclear>na</unclear>ka-<num value="1">pāṭaka</num> tīsanāda-jayadatta-kaṭake droṇi-maṭhikāyāṁ <num value="1">pāṭaka</num><g type="danda">.</g> I<unclear>t</unclear><supplied reason="lost">y</supplied> <unclear>e</unclear><supplied reason="lost">vaṁ na</supplied><lb 
                     n="11" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">ve</supplied>ṣu pāṭakeṣu <num value="10">daśa</num>-droṇādhikeṣu samupagata-viṣayapatī<supplied reason="omitted">n</supplied> kuṭumvinaś ca samā<supplied reason="lost">jnāpayati</supplied>
                 </p>
                 <p>
                     <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">vi</supplied>ditam astu bhavatāṁ Ete <num>daśa</num>-droṇādhika-<num value="9">nava</num>-pāṭakā yathā-bhuñjanād a<supplied reason="lost">panīya</supplied><lb 
                     n="13"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="1"/>-rājarājabhaṭṭasyāyuṣ-kāmārthaṁ Ācārya-vandya-saṁghamittra-pādai<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> kāri<unclear>ta</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ka</supplied><lb 
                     n="14" break="no"/>-<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="1"/>dvīpa-vihāra-vihārikā-<num value="4">catuṣṭayam</num> <num value="1">eka</num>-gaṇḍī-kṛtaṁ tad viṣayapaty-ādi-<unclear>ku</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ṭumvi</supplied><lb n="15" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">bhir ni</supplied><unclear>rāvādhai</unclear>r bhavitavyam iti
                 </p>
                 <p>samvaT <num value="13">10 3</num> vaiśākha di <num value="13">10 3</num></p>
                 <lg n="3" met="vasantatilakā">
                     <l n="a">Āyuś calaṁ <seg met="---+"><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="4"/></seg><lb n="16"/> <seg met="--"><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/></seg><unclear>ṇām a</unclear>bhogā</l>
                     <l n="b">puṇyaṁ ca sarva-gati duḥkha-bhayāpahāri<supplied reason="omitted"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied></l>
                     <l n="c">bhūme<choice><sic>ñ</sic><corr>ś</corr></choice> ca dānam i<seg met="-+-"><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/></seg><lb n="17"/><seg met="-+-"><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/></seg> vu<supplied reason="omitted">d</supplied>dhvā</l>
                     <l n="d">bhogīśvaraiḥ sa-karaṇaiḥ pratipālanīyam<unclear>·</unclear><choice><sic><g type="danda">.</g></sic><corr><g type="ddanda">.</g></corr></choice></l>
                 </lg>
                 <p>
                     dūtako <supplied reason="omitted">’</supplied>tra paramasau<supplied reason="lost">gata</supplied>-<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/><lb 
                     n="18"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/><supplied reason="lost">li</supplied>khitaṁ jayakarmānta-vāsake pa<unclear>rama</unclear>saugatopāsaka-pūradāse<unclear>ne</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ti</supplied>
                 </p>
